{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act37side", "eventName": "追跡日落以西", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GO-9", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "英雄的落幕", "storyInfo": "維娜送別了那位愛著維多利亞這個國家的竊冠者，並為她講述了一個真假難辨的故事——故事的主角維娜在戰爭勝利之後拒絕了王座上的阿利斯泰爾二世的加冕。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G1_interrogat_room", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>城防軍臨時監禁室</><p=2>1098年12月25日 8:32 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——2區總算打掃乾淨了，接下來就只剩4區了。怎麼樣，值班不輕鬆吧？要不要休息一下？", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打掃的速度可不比你慢。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是你，不用因為我是感染者就特意讓著我。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，倒不是這樣啦。只是覺得你經歷了這麼多，應該滿累的吧？", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我還以為——呵，至於王冠那件事，我早就想清楚了。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一時衝動嘛！加上有這個想法的可不只你一個。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過說起來，感覺一夜之間大家對感染者的態度沒那麼恐懼了。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是因為我們在倫蒂尼姆。議會和議長閣下推行的政策至少讓許多人不再把恐懼和厭惡掛在臉上。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但據我那位哥倫比亞的朋友說，其他地方還是老樣子。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不管怎麼說，謝謝你幫忙打掃，不然隊長又要罰我了。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是我該謝謝你們，至少沒有把我當犯人一樣關著。能做點事，反而讓我安心一點。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說啊，你根本不用擔心議會怎麼處置你。不然倫蒂尼姆這麼多能關人的地方，為什麼偏偏把你安置在城防軍的禁閉室？", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說白了，就是因為這裡的人不是老戰友就是老熟人，能幫忙照顧你啊。放心，等這幾天風頭過了，隨便找個藉口你就能回家了。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些還專門去議長辦公室抗議的人才是真看不懂局勢，維娜老大的為人我們還不清楚嗎？", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？不舒服嗎？要不要先休息一下？", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說……議長會放了我？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你就安安心心暫時在這避風頭吧。為了你那件事，外面現在可是鬧得沸沸揚揚。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長不讓我們給你收音機和報紙，就是怕你聽了之後胡思亂想。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，要是你實在緊張的話，我那個愛喝酒、三天兩頭被關禁閉的兄弟在這裡藏了點好東西。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，我拿點給你。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安苦笑，試圖聆聽外面的聲音。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但除了水流經過管道的聲音，她只能隱隱約約聽見城防軍操練的號令。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自從被關進這裡，她幾乎與外界失去了聯絡。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不知道埃利西奧先生還好嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真該提前和他說一聲。他現在應該很擔心我……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，他幾乎找遍了所有自己認識的人為你求情。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議長閣下……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#6$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好，他們沒有把你當犯人對待。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是您的安排嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，是大家自發的，他們認為你不該受到這樣的判決。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多人為了你的事來找過我，你的朋友、我的朋友……還有我們共同的戰友，甚至那些與你素未謀面的市民。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——黛安，我偷了點那小子藏的好酒！", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他仰頭灌下一口。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噗！", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵還沒走到黛安與維娜的面前，身體就僵住了。而嘴裡的酒，吐也不是，吞也不是。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只能尷尬地藏起手裡的酒瓶，站得筆直，向維娜行了個軍禮。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯——", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕特爾，別藏了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得號角小姐說過，軍營裡禁酒。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（吞下）咳——咳——", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，維娜老大！可，這不是……呃……", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以不告訴號角小姐，但你也得替我保密我來見黛安的事。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，酒放下吧，這是為黛安準備的，不是嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……好吧。維娜老大，你專門來找黛安就是為了她的後續安排吧？", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看吧，黛安，我就說不用擔心！", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就先去清理4區了。今天我可是老老實實執勤了一整天，什麼都不知道。", "name": "勤快的守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕特爾留下的酒，你想嚐嚐嗎？聞起來還不錯。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安低落地搖了搖頭。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那介意我先來一口嗎？唉，和那幾個公爵開會，說得我口乾舌燥。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議長閣下，您把我安排在這裡真的是為了要……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們希望至少讓你待在老朋友身邊會讓你好過一點。而且你也不希望我那麼做，對吧？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是的。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我沒有你想的那麼堅決。我過去的生活，和你，和大多數倫蒂尼姆人並無太大區別。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安，我的確猶豫過。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以您這次來是因為我的處置已經有了定論？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——我想我必須親自告訴你議會的決定，以及……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應當與你告別。原聯軍第六縱隊第十步兵團中尉黛安·韋伯——當之無愧的戰爭英雄。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你為了我們的家園所付出的一切。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議會嗎……我知道了，議長閣下。什麼時候？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你後悔過嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您呢？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許最後悔的事，是當初打完仗沒有馬上脫下這身衣服直接躲回諾伯特區。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，您不會的，我瞭解您。推進之王不會放棄我們的家鄉，倫蒂尼姆議長也放不下維多利亞。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈哈。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不後悔。維娜——我可以這樣稱呼您嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們見過很多次，也並肩作戰過很多次。但今天恐怕才是我們真正算得上朋友的一天。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，在我走之前，可以陪我喝一杯嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時，你獨自走進聖王會西部大堂，所有人都以為從那扇門走出來的會是一位頭戴王冠的人。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“英雄終當加冕為王。”", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在貝克街的那家老書店，每一本童話故事裡幾乎都有這麼一個橋段。那是我入伍前最愛去的地方。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，我也曾真心渴望見證歷史。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我讓你失望了，讓很多人失望了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是的，你本可以成為一位優秀的君王。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就因為我是個想讓倫蒂尼姆變得更好的人？那位被公開處決的國王難道不也是想讓倫蒂尼姆，讓維多利亞變得更好嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可往往總是事與願違。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時候，你認為的對，在別人眼裡卻是錯的。直到最近我才真正明白這一點。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那應該怎麼做？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也在尋找答案，黛安。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位我信任的人告訴我，要學會接受那些憎恨我的人，並堅守自己所相信的正義——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也還在學習……只是我從未想過，這條路會如此孤獨。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你醉了……維娜。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜搖了搖頭。她緩緩抽出自己的劍，遞到黛安的手中。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得“諸王之息”嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，那是你親手交給我的劍。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一戰之後，它徹底失去了鋒芒。於是工匠們日以繼夜地重鑄它，然後把它送給了我。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把新的劍比之前更沉重，因為它承載的期許也更多了……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安，這柄劍每天都在提醒我，什麼才是正確的方向——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但真正能確保維多利亞走在正確道路上的，不是我，也不是議會，而是你們。是那些親手奪回家園、選擇守護這片土地的人。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……維娜，我還有最後一個疑惑。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時，你在聖王會西部大堂裡到底經歷了什麼？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你希望聽到一個怎樣的故事——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個會在貝克街老書店流傳的英雄童話？還是一個真實到讓人厭倦的現實？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#8$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安她仰頭灌了一口酒，手掌輕輕撫過冰冷的劍身。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我更喜歡之前那把……握著它砍倒敵人的時候，我覺得那是我和維多利亞最親近的時刻。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "入伍前過得平平淡淡的時候，我怎麼也想不到會有這麼奇怪的想法……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我也沒有什麼時間去細細回味過去還沒打仗時的平靜生活了，不是嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，抱歉，這最後一口酒，我不能留給你了。我很需要它——", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哽咽）怎麼會在這個時候，我反倒開始怕死了。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#5$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哽咽）維娜，在我完全醉倒前再為我講最後一個童話吧。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#5$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "淚水順著劍鋒滑落。“滴答”、“滴答”。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安……過去的故事，你都聽過了。那段童話最精彩的部分，你也曾親身經歷過。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這個故事的結局，你或許還不知道。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天我走進了聖王會西部大堂，扯下薩卡茲的旗幟後準備離開，卻突然聽到了王座廳裡有人叫我的名字——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“亞歷山德莉娜·維娜·維多利亞。”", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後我推開了那扇已經塵封了已久的門。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見到了——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "55_i11", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 450.0, "yTo": 130.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.8, "yScaleFrom": 1.8, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chernobog_intro", "key": "$chernobog_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我的父親——阿利斯泰爾二世，他在對我說話。”"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的亞歷山德莉娜，你終於回家了。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的女兒，到我身邊來。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "55_i11", "fadetime": 3.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜看不清國王的面龐。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金色的面具與他金色的頭髮融為一體，威嚴而不可捉摸。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他，即維多利亞。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的女兒，你在害怕我嗎？還是在害怕維多利亞？", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，永遠不要在你的臣民面前露出任何一絲恐懼。你的老師應當教過你。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你已經死了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十六年前，他們把你吊死在了絞刑架上——", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可笑，誰能殺死維多利亞！", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些貪婪的禿鷹妄圖撕下我的血肉來填飽自己的胃口。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們懼怕王權，於是設計謀害自己的君主，只為能夠更加肆無忌憚地刮取阿斯蘭的土地、資源與養分。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可無人能殺死我們，公爵不行，紅龍也不行。我們就是維多利亞的心臟！", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是諸王長眠之所裡你的雕像從未完工的原因……", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵們根本沒有將你安葬，你一直都在這裡。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們只敢將我囚禁於這座王座廳，卻不敢染指我的王座分毫。哈哈，懦弱的竊國賊們。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們害怕我的子民，害怕我的蒸汽騎士，他們害怕我們，維娜。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女兒，告訴我——我的子民是否還懷念我？我的騎士是否仍然守衛著我們的王宮？", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……維多利亞人早已習慣了沒有國王的日子。而你的騎士，他們都死了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死在維多利亞人自己的手中。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，那你呢？", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……已經快忘記你的樣貌了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就走到我面前，摘下我的面具仔細看看……你只會看到你自己，亞歷山德莉娜，我們都流淌著王室的血。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，孩子，我未能實現我的諾言。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本想將一個安寧且強大的維多利亞交到你手中，如今卻因為背叛而在這王座上枯坐了二十餘年。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我終於還是等到了你。孩子，接過我的權杖，戴上我的冠冕……", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向我們的子民宣告，他們的國王回來了。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掃清這片國土上的一切叛亂與污穢，懲戒那些背叛王室的懦夫。榮光不滅，維多利亞當如此！", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dropspanner", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinbuckethit", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "國王的權杖重重地砸在王座台上，低沉的迴響在大堂內回盪，久久不絕。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……血脈從來都不是我們力量的來源。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼熟悉的話語。我年輕時也曾這麼對我的父親說過。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你還太過年輕，女兒，容我為你上這遲來的一課——“何為王權”。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我會賜予你反駁我的權力。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "亞歷山德莉娜，回到我的身邊，聆聽吧。", "name": "阿利斯泰爾二世"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你已經死了，陛下。如今這些，都不過是你沉溺於帝國榮光的迴響罷了。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無需你賜予我任何權力，我也無需向你證明我的信念有多堅定。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……父親，我只希望你安息。", "name": "維娜"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜握緊手中的戰錘，踏上台階，迎向帝國最後的餘暉。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}